# HashiCorp Cloud Platform (HCP) Provider

The HCP provider provides resources to manage [HashiCorp Cloud Platform](https://www.hashicorp.com/cloud-platform) (HCP) resources.

## Authenticating with HCP
The HCP provider accepts client credentials, which can be obtained on the creation of a service principle key. Service principles and service principle keys can be created on the Access Control (IAM) page.

